{"word":"G3965 - πατριά - patriá - pat-ree-ah' - Family","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πατριά</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">patriá</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pat-ree-ah'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Family</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"வம்சம், குடும்பம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. lineage running back to some progenitor, ancestry"},{"paragraph":"2. a race or tribe"},{"paragraph":"3. to nation, people"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>As if feminine of a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3962 - πατήρ - patḗr - pat-ayr'/3962\">G3962</a>; paternal <i>descent</i>, that is, (concretely) a <i>group</i> of families or a whole <i>race</i> (<i>nation</i>): - family, kindred, lineage.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3962/3962\">G3962</a>, <a href=\"#/G3965/3965\">G3965</a>, <a href=\"#/G3966/3966\">G3966</a>, <a href=\"#/G3967/3967\">G3967</a>, <a href=\"#/G3968/3968\">G3968</a>, <a href=\"#/G3971/3971\">G3971</a>, <a href=\"#/G540/540\">G540</a>"}]}